com.lambda.entity
Class Entity

java.lang.Object
  com.lambda.entity.Entity

public abstract class Entity
extends java.lang.Object

The 'Entity' is a representation of an 'Object' in the Game. 'Entities' can be rendered to the screen and updated.

Author:
alex
